title: The Epic Rocky Horror Collection - Music
description:
A continuing collection of Rocky Horror media.

Audio: (all MP3 format)
-The Rocky Horror Show (1973 London original cast recording)
-The Rocky Horror Show (1974 Roxy cast recording)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show (soundtrack)
-Shock Treatment (soundtrack)
-The Rocky Horror Show: The Whole Gory Story (1990 London revival cast recording)
-Songs from the Vaults: A Collection of Rocky Horror Rarities
-The Rocky Horror Show (2000 Broadway revival cast recording)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show: Sing It! (Karaoke instrumentals)
-The Rocky Horror Picture Show: 25th Anniversary (2000 re-release of the soundtrack with foreign covers)
-The Rocky Horror Punk Rock Show
-The Rocky Horror Glee Show (covers from the Glee episode)
-Songs from The Rocky Horror Picture Show (A 2012 live album by The Polyphonic Spree)

Because BitLord's torrent creator was being an asshole, the video files were uploaded separately.
